<br>
Few, especially those that play the Wizard class, think the current Mana Burn is a skill worth using or having.<br>
<br>
Some are even upset that SKs seem to have the same level of power that we had, which was supposedly imbalanced, for the investment of more AA points.  AA points are much easier to earn with the introduction of PoP, super duper ZEMs, high level mobs, and /raid shared exp.<br>
<br>
Clearly it would be remarkable if there was a new AA ability introduced that augmented, or somehow made Mana burn a viable tool and re-made it into a class defining ability...but the difficulties of maintaining balance and the apparent interest Sony has at capping and controlling the maximum power of player characters makes this very unlikely to happen.<br>
<br>
Again, my vote is that they either introduce another AA ability that influences the value of Mana Burn (perhaps even just an ability to lower the Mana Burn refresh timer), or retroactively fix the nerfing they did.  If they simply coded it so that AA criticals were again capable with Mana Burn I think everyone would be pleased.  If they did this alone, all they would be doing is giving those that have invested several AA in the Fury line the ability to reach the damage cap 20% more often.  This isn't alot to ask. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=26274.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=26274.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=26274.topic&start=61&stop=69>4</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=26274.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=26274.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26274.topic&index=40><img src=http://www.graffe.com/images/messageboard/add_reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=26274.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.threadControl?topicID=26274.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=